\shape italic
Differential Equations in Applied Mathematics
\shape default
 at Northwestern University. 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
J.J. Hoyt's chapter on the 
\shape italic
Mathematics of Diffusion
\shape default
 in his 
\shape italic
Phase Transformations
\shape default
 text. 
\end_layout

